final_map <- function(location, name_gu){
  com_bus <- buslocation %>% filter( == name_gu)
  com_caffe <- seoul_caffe %>% filter(area == name_gu)
  com_trash <- trash_bymarket2 %>% filter( == name_gu)
  com_trash$x <- as.numeric(as.character(com_trash$x)); com_trash$y <- as.numeric(as.character(com_trash$y))
  
  com_map <- get_map(location, source="google", maptype="roadmap", zoom = 16)
  ggmap(com_map) +   #  
    geom_point(data = com_caffe, aes(x=lon, y=lat), size=8, alpha = 0.5, color = "yellow") +   #  
    geom_point(data = com_trash, aes(x=x, y=y), size=8, color = "black", fill = "purple", shape = 21) +   #  
    geom_point(data = com_bus, aes(x=X, y=Y, size = ), alpha = 0.5, color = "forestgreen") +   #  
    scale_size_continuous(range=c(10,30)) +
    theme(legend.position = 'none')
}
